#

Savory Pork Gravy with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$12.99
620 kcal

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodFamily MealSavoryHearty

Description

Rich and hearty pork gravy served over creamy garlic mashed potatoes, perfect for comfort food lovers!

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 2 lbs
  • Onion: 1 medium, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Flour: 3 tbsp
  • Thyme: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Potatoes: 4 large
  • Sour cream: 1/2 cup
